软件包 com.taobao.datax.engine.storage

类摘要
DoubleQueue A import class in DataX, represents a region with two swap spaces, one for storing data which from data source, the other one for storing data which will be transfered to data destination.
FileStorage  
NULLStorage  
RAMStorage A concrete storage which use RAM memory space to store the swap spaces.
RouteStorage  
Storage A buffer where Reader and Writer exchange data.
StorageFactory As its name, This class produce storage space.
StoragePool StoragePool manages multiple storages.
